<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>国土报最新头条</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Wed, 25 Oct 2023 08:09:23 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>真主党主席会见黎巴嫩哈马斯和伊斯兰圣战组织领导人，讨论“加沙真正胜利”的方法</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-25/ty-article/.premium/hezbollah-chief-meets-with-hamas-islamic-jihad-leaders-in-lebanon-talk-gaza-victory/0000018b-65ac-d288-afef-f5fc701d0000</link><description>这次会议召开之际，以色列和黎巴嫩激进组织之间的紧张局势加剧，以色列北部边境的战斗有可能进一步升级，目前已经造成 6 名以色列士兵和 1 名平民死亡，据报道还有 40 名真主党成员死亡</description><pubDate>Wed, 25 Oct 2023 07:49:07 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-25/ty-article/.premium/hezbollah-chief-meets-with-hamas-islamic-jihad-leaders-in-lebanon-talk-gaza-victory/0000018b-65ac-d288-afef-f5fc701d0000</guid></item><item><title>据报道反犹太主义激增，美国犹太人在以色列与哈马斯战争的恐惧气氛中面临暴力威胁</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/jewish/2023-10-25/ty-article/antisemitism-spikes-and-u-s-jews-face-violence-amid-climate-of-fear-over-israel-hamas-war/0000018b-65a7-d288-afef-f5ff0cc00000</link><description>反诽谤联盟表示，哈马斯 10 月 7 日袭击以色列后，他们总共追踪到了 193 起反犹太主义事件，其中在美国增加了 21%； ADL 极端主义中心副总裁表示，“感觉就像纯粹的恐慌模式”</description><pubDate>Wed, 25 Oct 2023 07:38:31 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/jewish/2023-10-25/ty-article/antisemitism-spikes-and-u-s-jews-face-violence-amid-climate-of-fear-over-israel-hamas-war/0000018b-65a7-d288-afef-f5ff0cc00000</guid></item><item><title>以色列军队：伊朗通过情报共享帮助哈马斯；哈马斯高级指挥官在加沙地带被杀</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-25/ty-article-live/israel-strikes-syrian-military-targets-biden-israel-will-decide-about-gaza-ground-op/0000018b-6479-d473-a5fb-64f9518e0000</link><description>真主党纳斯鲁拉在黎巴嫩会见伊斯兰圣战组织和哈马斯领导人 ■ 红新月会报告称，以色列对杰宁的空袭造成两人死亡 ■ 五小时平静后，加沙的火箭弹再次发射 ■ 据叙利亚官方媒体报道，以色列对军事阵地的空袭造成八名叙利亚军事人员死亡 ■自 10 月 7 日以来，至少有 1,300 人被哈马斯杀害 ■ 哈马斯管理的卫生部：5,300 名巴勒斯坦人被杀，18,000 人受伤</description><pubDate>Wed, 25 Oct 2023 04:33:58 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-25/ty-article-live/israel-strikes-syrian-military-targets-biden-israel-will-decide-about-gaza-ground-op/0000018b-6479-d473-a5fb-64f9518e0000</guid></item><item><title>疏忽大意的内塔尼亚胡为政治生存而战，拒绝面对以色列公众</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-25/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-battles-for-survival-as-the-head-of-israels-endless-fiasco-government/0000018b-6344-ddfd-a59f-e3e43f800000</link><description>在战争最激烈的时期，内塔尼亚胡已经在为第二天做准备，并试图操纵调查委员会。他还没有鼓起勇气面对以色列媒体，但却花了至少一半的时间来确保他的王位稳固</description><pubDate>Wed, 25 Oct 2023 03:00:08 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-25/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-battles-for-survival-as-the-head-of-israels-endless-fiasco-government/0000018b-6344-ddfd-a59f-e3e43f800000</guid></item><item><title>国土报卡通</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/daily-cartoon/2023-10-25/ty-article-opinion/haaretz-cartoon/0000018b-63ec-d230-a1bf-6bfd34d30000</link><description></description><pubDate>Tue, 24 Oct 2023 23:03:38 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/daily-cartoon/2023-10-25/ty-article-opinion/haaretz-cartoon/0000018b-63ec-d230-a1bf-6bfd34d30000</guid></item><item><title>以色列对加沙的地面入侵将会发生。何时以及如何取决于拜登</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-25/ty-article/.premium/israels-ground-invasion-of-gaza-will-happen-the-when-and-how-depends-on-biden/0000018b-6344-d288-afef-f3dc404a0000</link><description>美国总统正在给以色列时间——如果以色列做得正确的话——但是，在 10 月 7 日事件之后，内塔尼亚胡不再相信以色列国防军的能力。加沙地面行动可能会被搁置几天以上</description><pubDate>Tue, 24 Oct 2023 21:43:33 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-25/ty-article/.premium/israels-ground-invasion-of-gaza-will-happen-the-when-and-how-depends-on-biden/0000018b-6344-d288-afef-f3dc404a0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列外长向人质家属施压，要求其取消与联合国秘书长的会面</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-24/ty-article/.premium/israeli-fm-pressured-families-of-hostages-to-cancel-meeting-with-un-secretary-general/0000018b-6374-d473-a5fb-67fd89090000</link><description>在联合国秘书长表示哈马斯 10 月 7 日的袭击“并非凭空发生”后，伊莱·科恩取消了与安东尼奥·古特雷斯的会面。</description><pubDate>Tue, 24 Oct 2023 20:59:21 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-24/ty-article/.premium/israeli-fm-pressured-families-of-hostages-to-cancel-meeting-with-un-secretary-general/0000018b-6374-d473-a5fb-67fd89090000</guid></item><item><title>在摧毁哈马斯之前释放人质</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2023-10-24/ty-article-opinion/.premium/freeing-the-hostages-comes-before-destroying-hamas/0000018b-62e0-d473-a5fb-66e9382d0000</link><description></description><pubDate>Tue, 24 Oct 2023 20:19:54 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2023-10-24/ty-article-opinion/.premium/freeing-the-hostages-comes-before-destroying-hamas/0000018b-62e0-d473-a5fb-66e9382d0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列政府也正在放弃经济</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/editorial/2023-10-24/ty-article-opinion/israels-government-is-abandoning-the-economy-too/0000018b-6306-ddfd-a59f-e3e6dacb0000</link><description></description><pubDate>Tue, 24 Oct 2023 20:18:19 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/editorial/2023-10-24/ty-article-opinion/israels-government-is-abandoning-the-economy-too/0000018b-6306-ddfd-a59f-e3e6dacb0000</guid></item><item><title>释放以色列人质的言论被政府官员视为损害以色列利益</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-24/ty-article/.premium/freed-hostages-remarks-were-seen-by-government-as-damaging-to-israeli-interests/0000018b-628c-d288-afef-f2dc7ad60000</link><description>约切韦德·利夫希茨 (Yocheved Lifshitz) 声称她“获得了医疗护理”并“在被囚禁期间得到了良好的待遇”，这让官员们担心，这可能会损害国际社会释放剩余人质的努力</description><pubDate>Tue, 24 Oct 2023 18:35:32 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-24/ty-article/.premium/freed-hostages-remarks-were-seen-by-government-as-damaging-to-israeli-interests/0000018b-628c-d288-afef-f2dc7ad60000</guid></item><item><title>以色列领导人猛烈抨击联合国秘书长称哈马斯袭击“并非凭空发生”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-24/ty-article/.premium/israel-slams-un-secretary-general-for-saying-hamas-attack-did-not-occur-in-a-vacuum/0000018b-6279-d230-a1bf-6bf965790000</link><description>以色列联盟和反对派成员在社交媒体上严厉谴责联合国秘书长安东尼奥·古特雷斯为哈马斯的暴行辩护，一些人要求他辞职</description><pubDate>Tue, 24 Oct 2023 18:15:41 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-24/ty-article/.premium/israel-slams-un-secretary-general-for-saying-hamas-attack-did-not-occur-in-a-vacuum/0000018b-6279-d230-a1bf-6bf965790000</guid></item><item><title>我们可以从被释放的哈马斯人质约切韦德·利夫什茨身上学到什么</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2023-10-24/ty-article/.highlight/what-we-can-learn-from-released-hamas-hostage-yocheved-lifshitz/0000018b-6282-d288-afef-f2dac6180000</link><description>约切维德·利夫希茨刚刚经历了世上很少有人能够理解的创伤。尤其是在作为一个自由女性的最初几天，尤其是当她拾起生活中剩下的碎片时，我们不应该评判她处理它的方式</description><pubDate>Tue, 24 Oct 2023 17:40:16 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2023-10-24/ty-article/.highlight/what-we-can-learn-from-released-hamas-hostage-yocheved-lifshitz/0000018b-6282-d288-afef-f2dac6180000</guid></item><item><title>布林肯敦促国际社会对哈马斯袭击表示愤怒</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-24/ty-article/.premium/blinken-urges-world-leaders-to-express-outrage-over-hamas-attacks-after-un-controversy/0000018b-626e-d230-a1bf-6bff23fd0000</link><description>“我们谁也无法想象他们所经历的噩梦。美国国务卿安东尼·布林肯在谈到人质家属时表示，这是任何家庭都不应该忍受的事情，其中​​几人出席了一次罕见的联合国安理会部长级会议</description><pubDate>Tue, 24 Oct 2023 16:53:33 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-24/ty-article/.premium/blinken-urges-world-leaders-to-express-outrage-over-hamas-attacks-after-un-controversy/0000018b-626e-d230-a1bf-6bff23fd0000</guid></item><item><title>这是内塔尼亚胡最灾难性的错误</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-24/ty-article-opinion/.premium/this-was-netanyahus-most-catastrophic-error/0000018b-611a-d307-adbb-653a04980000</link><description>内塔尼亚胡在哈马斯发动卑鄙袭击之前所犯的所有错误中，从攻击以色列民主到个人腐败，从拥抱普京到扶植极端分子，他将巴勒斯坦人拒之门外的战略是一场灾难 — — 并且削弱了以色列可能获得的全球民众支持预期的</description><pubDate>Tue, 24 Oct 2023 15:57:13 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-24/ty-article-opinion/.premium/this-was-netanyahus-most-catastrophic-error/0000018b-611a-d307-adbb-653a04980000</guid></item><item><title>“我没有时间让这种痛苦进入我的脑海。我不能被打败&amp;#39;</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-24/ty-article-magazine/.premium/i-dont-have-time-to-let-this-pain-get-inside-my-head-i-cant-be-defeated/0000018b-61d3-d473-a5fb-65db97b00000</link><description>被哈马斯扣为人质的以色列家庭：一个特别项目 ■ 当她的哥哥 Roi 被谋杀时，Ayelet Svatitzky 的母亲 Channah 和弟弟 Nadav 被哈马斯绑架。 “我的任务是带他们回家，”阿耶莱特说</description><pubDate>Tue, 24 Oct 2023 15:21:21 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-24/ty-article-magazine/.premium/i-dont-have-time-to-let-this-pain-get-inside-my-head-i-cant-be-defeated/0000018b-61d3-d473-a5fb-65db97b00000</guid></item><item><title>古生物学家推断出 4.65 亿年前三叶虫午餐吃什么</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/science/2023-10-24/ty-article/paleontologists-deduce-what-a-trilobite-ate-for-lunch-465-million-years-ago/0000018b-620c-ddfd-a59f-e3ec3a860000</link><description>据信三叶虫在寒武纪海底相当不加区别地进食</description><pubDate>Tue, 24 Oct 2023 15:16:17 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/science/2023-10-24/ty-article/paleontologists-deduce-what-a-trilobite-ate-for-lunch-465-million-years-ago/0000018b-620c-ddfd-a59f-e3ec3a860000</guid></item><item><title>伊朗对跨越红线持谨慎态度，可能会让加沙独自战斗</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/iran/2023-10-24/ty-article/.premium/iran-is-wary-of-crossing-red-lines-and-could-leave-gaza-to-fight-alone/0000018b-5b4b-d2b2-addf-7f7b01d60000</link><description>德黑兰知道，直接军事对抗可能会终止重启核协议的谈判，甚至在无法依赖俄罗斯军事支持的情况下导致直接攻击。到目前为止，它还没有表现出打算积极、直接参与战争的迹象</description><pubDate>Tue, 24 Oct 2023 15:11:29 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/iran/2023-10-24/ty-article/.premium/iran-is-wary-of-crossing-red-lines-and-could-leave-gaza-to-fight-alone/0000018b-5b4b-d2b2-addf-7f7b01d60000</guid></item><item><title>在加州湾区：加沙人质家人的痛苦等待</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/jewish/2023-10-24/ty-article/in-califonias-bay-area-an-agonizing-wait-for-families-of-gaza-hostages/0000018b-6192-d8e2-a1eb-e39697e00000</link><description>加沙人质的亲属焦急地等待被俘家庭成员的最新消息。一名示威者说：“已经两周了，时间已经不多了”</description><pubDate>Tue, 24 Oct 2023 14:30:37 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/jewish/2023-10-24/ty-article/in-califonias-bay-area-an-agonizing-wait-for-families-of-gaza-hostages/0000018b-6192-d8e2-a1eb-e39697e00000</guid></item><item><title>与哈马斯关于释放加沙人质的谈判正在取得进展，但仍没有突破</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-24/ty-article/.premium/talks-with-hamas-on-release-of-gaza-hostages-are-advancing-but-still-no-breakthrough/0000018b-6188-d473-a5fb-65c915cb0000</link><description>目前尚不清楚以色列需要为释放大量人质付出什么代价（如果有的话）。哈马斯可能以释放巴勒斯坦安全囚犯为条件达成协议，或坚持要求更多人道主义援助和燃料箱进入加沙地带</description><pubDate>Tue, 24 Oct 2023 14:23:32 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-24/ty-article/.premium/talks-with-hamas-on-release-of-gaza-hostages-are-advancing-but-still-no-breakthrough/0000018b-6188-d473-a5fb-65c915cb0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列和加沙战争升级到底意味着什么</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-24/ty-article/.premium/what-does-the-escalation-of-the-israel-gaza-war-really-mean/0000018b-60cc-d8e2-a1eb-e3de165c0000</link><description>媒体充斥着“垂直升级”和“水平升级”等词语，但它们在以色列、加沙、真主党和伊朗的背景下到底意味着什么 — — 以及为什么美国如此担心？</description><pubDate>Tue, 24 Oct 2023 13:52:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-24/ty-article/.premium/what-does-the-escalation-of-the-israel-gaza-war-really-mean/0000018b-60cc-d8e2-a1eb-e3de165c0000</guid></item></channel></rss>